Responsibilities
Mid-level/Senior business analyst with strong functional/business analysis skills with experience in Salesforce
Engage with stakeholders to understand requirement and break down into user stories
Coordinate with QA team and answer QA queries and Organize & refine the user stories in backlog
Work with clients and end users to collect, understand, and define business requirements.
Participate in key meetings with clients including requirement sessions, system demos, user acceptance testing, and end user training.
Map the business requirement to the sales portfolio appropriate for clients.
Evaluate and incorporate new technologies into new and existing frameworks and solutions as applicable
Collaborate with and mentor members of the team and other coworkers
Be agile and accept change
Qualifications
Minimum qualifications
MBA
Robust analytics experience
Preferred qualifications
Experience in cost Model creation and management
Ability to handle pre-sales process management and execution
Prior experience in sales support
